Urho3D::StaticModelGroup Class Reference

Renders several object instances while culling and receiving light as one unit. Can be used as a CPU-side optimization, but note that also regular StaticModels will use instanced rendering if possible. More...

Detailed Description

Renders several object instances while culling and receiving light as one unit. Can be used as a CPU-side optimization, but note that also regular StaticModels will use instanced rendering if possible.
